    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Pick Me Pick Me》是一款独具创意的双人在线游戏，它将约会中可能发生的胡闹与欢乐带入了虚拟的世界。在这场约会大作战中，你将和对手展开创意比拼，通过与AI角色进行引人入胜的对话，展示独特的时尚品位，以及使用策略卡片来获取角色的青睐，击败对手，成为最终赢家。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras/8c09cded4be16f37d8f30c66eb7a9196.poster.avif?t=1749060718\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras/8c09cded4be16f37d8f30c66eb7a9196.webm?t=1749060718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras/21e098b8cb096c4964d806e008c92f10.avif?t=1749060718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras_big/21e098b8cb096c4964d806e008c92f10.avif?t=1749060718 width=800 height=288 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与好友直接竞争，参加节奏快速的极速约会对战！运用你的机智和策略破坏卡，击败对手，赢得那些奇特又难忘的AI角色的青睐。这是一场考验友谊和调情技巧的爆笑挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爱情即战争，调情需谨慎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras/ed2bfef411af0422f16018dac8db1ba3.poster.avif?t=1749060718\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras/ed2bfef411af0422f16018dac8db1ba3.webm?t=1749060718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras/5fe260d61cadc965ad29b63632b2e31c.avif?t=1749060718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras_big/5fe260d61cadc965ad29b63632b2e31c.avif?t=1749060718 width=800 height=288 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想练习游戏技巧，还是单纯享受数字浪漫？与20多个独特的AI角色一对一聊天——从油嘴滑舌的高手、可爱的怪咖，到拥有非常人类烦恼的奇幻生物，应有尽有。按自己的节奏建立关系，完全不受干扰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras/2ba4c2e01b6cf71f59581c914360f664.avif?t=1749060718\" width=616 height=440 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras/f3facaa7063fcaefab576201c0cff1ee.avif?t=1749060718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras_big/f3facaa7063fcaefab576201c0cff1ee.avif?t=1749060718 width=800 height=288 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不喜欢官方角色阵容？那就自己设计奇葩的约会对象吧！上传自定义模型，设定独特个性，用你的创作挑战朋友。将你最疯狂的角色分享给社区，让混乱持续焕新！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 主要特色</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态AI对话</strong>：每次游玩都能体验由大型语言模型驱动的独特实时互动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>20+可约会角色</strong>：邂逅拥有独特个性和故事的各色角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>跨平台游玩与存档</strong>：无论PC还是手机，随时随地与好友对战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略技能卡</strong>：强化自己或干扰对手的浪漫行动，带来爆笑结局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多语言匹配</strong>：支持英语、西班牙语、德语、法语、日语、韩语、简体中文、繁体中文和葡萄牙语，与全球好友一起畅玩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用户自创内容</strong>：通过创意工坊创建并分享你自己的角色，解锁无尽约会可能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全球排行榜</strong>：在混乱的极速约会场景中看看你的排名如何</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同语言的玩家也能一起畅玩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于《Pick Me Pick Me》支持多种语言，即使你和朋友不会说同一种语言，也能同场竞技。用你最熟悉的语言表达观点，挑战对手，无论他们说什么语言都不受影响！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras/a9e45d4c3d4c43c5229ca413123f414f.avif?t=1749060718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189430/extras_big/a9e45d4c3d4c43c5229ca413123f414f.avif?t=1749060718 width=800 height=288 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💸 免费试用 + 游戏内货币解锁</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开始免费试玩——每个人都能体验混乱的试用回合！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整体验需要购买游戏内货币（用于支付AI代币费用），以解锁无限制的约会对战、自定义角色、更深入的关系培养和高级剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是为了爱情、欢笑，还是追求浪漫的终极胜利，Pick Me Pick Me 都能带来难忘的混乱、魅力与喜剧的完美结合。凭借无限独特的AI互动、自定义内容和竞技元素，这是一场心智与情感的终极对决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以，准备好，滑动加入，让最荒诞的约会者赢得胜利吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
